<section class="about-section" id="about-section">
  <h2 class="about-title scroll-target-title">About Me</h2>
  <div class="about-content scroll-target-content">
    <p>
      This site is still under construction. It's under very active development, so every time you
      visit, there might be something new!
    </p>
    <p>Here's the pages you can find on this site:</p>
    <ul class="about-nav-list">
      <li>
        <a href="/timeline">Timeline</a>: A record of my experiences, listed in chronological order.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/resume">Résumé</a>: My résumé, including my education, experience, skills, and
        awards.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>: My projects, including my personal, class and hobby
        projects.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>: Contact me through email and social media.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 15vh 10%;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 2rem + 2vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  /* --- Styles for the navigation list --- */
